22#ifndef GCC_TREE_PRETTY_PRINT_H
23#define GCC_TREE_PRETTY_PRINT_H
24
25#include "pretty-print.h"
26
27#define pp_unsupported_tree(PP, T) \
28 pp_verbatim (PP, "#%qs not supported by %s#", \
29 get_tree_code_name (TREE_CODE (T)), __FUNCTION__)
30
31#define pp_ti_abstract_origin(TI) ((tree *) (TI)->x_data)
32
33
34extern void debug_generic_expr (tree);
35extern void debug_generic_stmt (tree);
36extern void debug_tree_chain (tree);
37extern void print_generic_decl (FILE *, tree, int);
38extern void print_generic_stmt (FILE *, tree, int);
39extern void print_generic_stmt_indented (FILE *, tree, int, int);
40extern void print_generic_expr (FILE *, tree, int);
41extern void dump_omp_clauses (pretty_printer *, tree, int, int);
42extern int dump_generic_node (pretty_printer *, tree, int, int, bool);
43extern void print_declaration (pretty_printer *, tree, int, int);
44extern int op_code_prio (enum tree_code);
45extern int op_prio (const_tree);
46extern const char *op_symbol_code (enum tree_code);
47extern void print_call_name (pretty_printer *, tree, int);
48extern void percent_K_format (text_info *);
49extern void pp_tree_identifier (pretty_printer *, tree);
50extern void dump_function_header (FILE *, tree, int);
51extern void pp_double_int (pretty_printer *pp, double_int d, bool uns);
52extern void dump_location (pretty_printer *buffer, location_t loc);

54#endif /* ! GCC_TREE_PRETTY_PRINT_H */
